reviews.review_text: Why Upload This One? Here's a source that can't be streamed, since it's 5.1 audio, and can't be downloaded because it is a soundboard.  What a waste of effort due to ignorance.

Foolish Mortals... *Any* show on this site can be easily downloaded if you know how....

You just gotta poke around.  ;-)

Thanks for the amazing sound quality !
